        ],
        "parameters": {
          "width": 740,
          "height": 100,
          "content": "## STEP 3 - MAIN FLOW\nStart the workflow manually or periodically by hooking the \"Schedule Trigger\" node. It is recommended to set it at 5 minute intervals."
        },
